NumTargets (script event)
=========================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game\_class) type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Returns the number of entities this entity has targeted.

Usage
-----

*float* numTargets()

Parameters
----------

This script event does not accept parameters.

Examples
--------

` `
`availTargets = `<font color="#000055">`$my_entity`</font>`.`<font color="#ff0000">`numTargets`</font><font color="#000000">`(`</font><font color="#000000">`)`</font>`;`

Notes
-----

This script event returns the number of entities this entity has targeted as a float.


